projects.name: Boid Behavior Demo
projects.desc: Made with Rust, Using Web Assembly and the Bevy Game Engine. This demo shows a model for boid behaviour, seen in the real world in structures such as schools of fish.

projects.name: Data Association Algorithms Comparison
projects.desc: Several data association algorithms implemented in Rust for benchmarking and comparison. The algorithms are Apriori, PCY, Multi Hash PCY, Ransom Sample Apriori, and SON.

projects.name: Web Development Group Project
projects.desc: A web application build using Vue in collaboration with 4 others in a web development class. Contains several video games.

projects.name: GeoPhoto Social Media Prototype
projects.desc: A mobile app made using the flutter framework in collaboration with 3 others in a mobile development class. It's a prototype social media site where users can post geo located photos on a map.

projects.name: Image Cartoonizer
projects.desc: Demonstration of using OpenCV for image processing in a jupyter notebook environment, using color flattening and canny edge detection.

projects.name: This Portfolio
projects.desc: Developed using React and Bootstrap. This project demonstrates topics like state management, asynchronous loading, and UI design.
